abstract: New York Red Bulls defeats China, 2-0, in Asian Cup; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: Cahill of the Red Bulls clinched a 2-0 win against China, helping Australia reach the semifinals of the Asian Cup in Brisbane, Australia.

headline.main: Tim Cahill’s Scissor Kick Propels Australia
